divs: sighting details[ text of witness email relayed to don burleson from stan friedman by way of john schuessler:] "my name is jose tapia. yesterday morning we spotted an object hovering from east to west over albuquerque skies, i grab my digital video camera and film, possible the best or only one of a kind video of this object crossing our skies at 6:45 a.m. on 7\20\06. i zoom in & out to video the object is amazing what i have on video. i try to reported to the center. i did not know to who to contact to how to market this exclusive video. please could you help."
